  "title": "Assistant Manager, Finance (Property Manager)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Prepare and maintain the accuracy and integrity of its private limited financial statements and financial processes, including cash flow monitoring and treasury related matters.</li><li>Lead corporate secretarial records, delegation of authority, and adherence to internal controls.</li><li>Assist in the preparation of management reporting and financial statements.</li><li>Preparation of tax and GST computation.</li><li>Assist in periodical financial reporting and ad hoc reports as required, and liaise with internal/external auditors/tax agents.</li></ul><p><strong>You should have:</strong></p><ul><li>Recognised Degree in Accountancy or equivalent professional qualification</li><li>A minimum of 5 years work experience, and familiarity with SFRS</li><li>Audit experience is preferred and prior experience working in a real estate or property management companies will be an added advantage</li><li>Meticulous and driven with strong analytical skills</li></ul><p><em>All applications will be treated in the strictest confidence. Personal data provided will be used for recruitment purposes only. </em></p><p>Please apply with your CV in word document format. We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. For other positions related to real estate or other alternative investments, please go to https://careers.tri-cap.com.sg/.</p><p>EA Licence: 24S2282 <br />​EA Personnel: R1107990</p>",
